;B[cm]LB[el:1][ek:2][dk:3][em:4][cl:5][fl:6][cm:7]C[Dia.1 The flower shape is 30 points

{\colortbl ;\red0\green0\blue255;\red255\green0\blue0;}
If Black attaches from the right, White will capture the one stone.  White plays 2, then Black will cut with 3, thinking that he'll be able to connect.

Up to 7, Black has allowed White to capture a stone in the center and create a flower shape towards the center.  White might think that since he only got one stone and Black connected under that this isn't a good result for him.  Nothing could be further from the truth.
\lang1042\f1\fs18
